            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Depositio Ursi die XI <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> Novembris <expan><abbr>indic</abbr><ex>tione</ex></expan> XV </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ursi tum<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>lum</abbr></expan> cernis <expan><abbr>quicumq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> viator <lb n="2"/>quem iuve&amp;lt;n=A&amp;gt;em rapuit sors ultima &amp;lt;p=T&amp;gt;erlege q<expan><ex>uae</ex><abbr>so</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/>qui vixit quinquaginta in annis heu m<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>sera</abbr></expan> Al<lb break="no" n="4"/>exandria gemit decepta marito qui est putita dul<lb break="no" n="5"/>cem coniugem viginti et sex annos et &amp;lt;m=N&amp;gt;emor eventos <lb n="6"/>alios mone vita brebis <note>sic</note> est cunctis fila parant et <expan><abbr>Parc</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="7"/>e nec parcetur ullis &amp;lt;n=H&amp;gt;unc illi dismisit <expan><abbr>duo</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> anxia natos <lb n="8"/>condicio talis omnem conplecitur urbem sed m<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>ritu</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="9"/>m et binefacta <note>sic</note> adiutant <expan><abbr>laborq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fidesq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> haecne libertum <lb n="10"/>dominis fecere probatum h<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>ecne</abbr></expan> defendunt senper <note>sic</note> sociant<lb break="no" n="11"/><expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> beatis si par esse belis <note>sic</note> similem mihi suscipe curam 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die erste Zeile der Inschrift befindet sich auf dem Sarkophagdeckel. Sarkophagkasten.</p>
            </div>
